#: ../../source/index.rst:2
msgid "Welcome to ISAT-SAM's documentation!"
msgstr "ISAT-SAM 문서에 오신 것을 환영합니다!"

#: ../../source/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"**ISAT-SAM** stands for Interactive Semi-Automatic Annotation Tool with "
"`Segment Anything Model <https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-"
"anything>`_"
msgstr ""
"**ISAT-SAM** 은 `Segment Anything Model "
"<https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything>`_ 이 포함된 대화형 반자동 주석 "
"도구를 나타냅니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:6
msgid ""
"You can `access the project "
"<https://github.com/yatengLG/ISAT_with_segment_anything>`_ on GitHub and "
"view the source code."
msgstr ""
"GitHub에서 `프로젝트 <https://github.com/yatengLG/ISAT_with_segment_anything>`_ 에 "
"접속하여 소스코드를 보실 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:-1
msgid "software.gif"
msgstr "software.gif"

#: ../../source/index.rst:12
msgid "Features"
msgstr "주요 기능"

#: ../../source/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"Focusing on the field of image segmentation, we strive to create the best "
"image segmentation annotation software."
msgstr "우리는 이미지 분할 분야에 중점을 두고 최고의 이미지 분할 주석 소프트웨어를 만들기 위해 노력하고 있습니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:16
msgid "Better performance and a smoother annotation experience."
msgstr "더 나은 성능과 더 매끄러운 주석 경험을 제공합니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"Supports `SAM <https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything>`_, "
"`SAM2 <https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything-2>`_, `SAM3 "
"<https://github.com/facebookresearch/sam3>`_, `Sam-HQ "
"<https://github.com/SysCV/sam-hq>`_, `MobileSAM "
"<https://github.com/ChaoningZhang/MobileSAM>`_, `EdgeSAM "
"<https://github.com/chongzhou96/EdgeSAM>`_ and `MedSAM "
"<https://github.com/bowang-lab/MedSAM>`_."
msgstr ""
"`SAM <https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything>`_, `SAM2 "
"<https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything-2>`_, `SAM3 "
"<https://github.com/facebookresearch/sam3>`_, `Sam-HQ "
"<https://github.com/SysCV/sam-hq>`_, `MobileSAM "
"<https://github.com/ChaoningZhang/MobileSAM>`_, `EdgeSAM "
"<https://github.com/chongzhou96/EdgeSAM>`_ 및 `MedSAM "
"<https://github.com/bowang-lab/MedSAM>`_ 을 지원합니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"Supports `Segment anything model "
"<https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything>`_ with ``point "
"prompt`` and ``box prompt`` to semi-automatic annotation."
msgstr ""
"반자동 주석에 ``point prompt`` 및 ``box prompt`` 을 사용하여 `Segment anything model "
"<https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything>`_ 을 지원합니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:19
msgid "Supports ``text prompt`` and ``visual prompt`` based on sam3."
msgstr "SAM3을 기반으로 ``text prompt`` 및 ``visual prompt`` 을 지원합니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:20
msgid "Supports using remote server for SAM encoding."
msgstr "SAM 인코딩에 원격 서버 사용을 지원합니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:21
msgid "Supports ``video annotation``."
msgstr "``video annotation`` 을 지원합니다."

#: ../../source/index.rst:22
msgid "Supports plugin extensions."
msgstr "plugin 확장을 지원합니다."

